\begin_inset space ~
\end_inset


\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "sub:Galaxy-scale-obscuration-for"

\end_inset

):
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{L_{\text{peak}}}{10^{43}\text{erg/s}} & =\left(\frac{M_{\text{BH}}}{M_{L43}}\right)^{\AP}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

Here, at 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{L43}$
\end_inset

 the distribution peaks at 
\begin_inset Formula $L(2-10\,{\rm keV})=10^{43}\text{erg/s}$
\end_inset

, which is 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{\text{bol}}=10^{10.7}L_{\bigodot}$
\end_inset

