\begin_inset Formula $0.66\,{\rm dex}$
\end_inset

 and a skew towards low masses 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand citep
key "WinterBAT2009"

\end_inset

.
 Adopting an appropriate skewed normal distribution with skew parameter
 
\begin_inset Formula $-10$
\end_inset

